					<h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Designed for software teams like yours</h2>
					<p class="mb-5 font-light text-gray-500 sm:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">Here at Flowbite we focus on markets where technology, innovation, and capital can unlock long-term value and drive economic growth.
